column4:
Dear [REDACTED] 

I hope this message finds you well. To ensure smooth processing of our financial transactions, 

I have shared a folder on SharePoint Online containing important accounts receivable documents, including invoices and payment confirmations.

Please review the documents and get back to me if there are any questions or concerns.
